{"analytics_identifier":"OT305","base_path":"/government/organisations/secret-intelligence-service","content_id":"aaa6186d-9753-4532-b500-6ab745045231","description":"The Secret Intelligence Service, often known as MI6, collects Britain’s foreign intelligence. It provides the government with a global covert capability to promote and defend the national security and economic well-being of the country. SIS works with the Foreign, Commonwealth & Development Office .","details":{"acronym":"SIS","alternative_format_contact_email":"","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Secret Intelligence Service, often known as MI6, collects Britain’s foreign intelligence. It provides the government with a global covert capability to promote and defend the national security and economic well-being of the country.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Secret Intelligence Service\">SIS</abbr> works with the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/foreign-commonwealth-development-office\">Foreign, Commonwealth &amp; Development Office</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"foreign-commonwealth-development-office","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Secret Intelligence Service"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[],"ordered_featured_documents":[],"ordered_featured_links":[],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"exempt","updated_at":null,"url":"https://www.sis.gov.uk/"},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"other","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"","social_media_links":[]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2012-02-10T11:19:44+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT305","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/secret-intelligence-service","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/secret-intelligence-service","base_path":"/government/organisations/secret-intelligence-service","content_id":"aaa6186d-9753-4532-b500-6ab745045231","document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-04-15T09:00:15Z","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Secret Intelligence Service","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/secret-intelligence-service","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_board_members":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/richard-moore","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/richard-moore","base_path":"/government/people/richard-moore","content_id":"853b8c68-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"image":{"alt_text":"Sir Richard Moore KCMG","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a4f6423e5274a6bf054e215/s465_RM3.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"e852d723-0b99-4a58-a959-9ca164d868e5","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":7380,"started_on":"2020-10-01T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"6329d5f3-dc35-4ae0-9d7f-811c975fc9eb","details":{"body":"<p>The Chief of the Secret Intelligence Service (known as MI6) is the only serving member of the service who is officially named in public.</p>\n\n<p>The role is appointed by and accountable to the <a href=\"/government/ministers/foreign-secretary\">Foreign Secretary</a>.</p>\n\n<p>The Chief is responsible for the control of MI6 operations and for the efficiency of the service. The role holder makes an annual report on the work of MI6 to the <a href=\"/government/ministers/prime-minister\">Prime Minister</a> and the Foreign Secretary.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2017-03-31T14:44:02Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief of the Secret Intelligence Service (SIS)","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-11-30T15:45:59Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Richard Moore CMG - Chief of the Secret Intelligence Service (SIS)","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"ae4e9a2b-9dd9-45d7-be87-0facb0ce0039","details":{"current":false,"ended_on":"2020-09-01T00:00:00+01:00","person_appointment_order":4730,"started_on":"2018-04-09T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"f393dd96-436b-410b-bb92-273e4a065c64","details":{"body":"<p>Board members give corporate leadership to the Foreign &amp; Commonwealth Office by ensuring that the department meets the foreign policy priorities, Public Service Agreements targets and service delivery targets set by ministers. The Director General, Political focuses on the UK’s key foreign policy objectives and has the following areas of responsibility and regions:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the Government’s foreign policy priorities, international crises and conflict, maintenance of international peace and security</li>\n  <li>European Union Common Foreign and Security Policy (CFSP) and Common Security and Defence Policy \n (CSDP)</li>\n  <li>the UK relationship with the United States</li>\n  <li>Middle East and North Africa</li>\n  <li>South Asia and Afghanistan</li>\n  <li>Western Balkans</li>\n  <li>Eastern Mediterranean</li>\n  <li>United Nations, including the UN Security Council, and other multilateral fora</li>\n</ul>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2018-12-18T10:38:46Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director General, Political","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2020-09-02T15:00:22Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Richard Moore CMG - Director General, Political","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"5dfbbf0c-7747-4eb8-b739-91010303d663","details":{"current":false,"ended_on":"2017-12-18T00:00:00+00:00","person_appointment_order":1630,"started_on":"2014-01-11T00:00:00+00:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"8464b7f5-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Ambassador represents His Majesty The King and the UK government in the country to which they are appointed. They are responsible for the direction and work of the Embassy and its Consulates, including political work, trade and investment, press and cultural relations, and visa and consular services.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"ambassador_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-07-26T11:35:45Z","schema_name":"role","title":"British Ambassador to Turkey","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-08-15T18:11:25Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Richard Moore CMG - British Ambassador to Turkey","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-06-19T11:25:29Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Sir Richard Moore KCMG","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/richard-moore","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_child_organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT1349","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/national-cyber-force","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/national-cyber-force","base_path":"/government/organisations/national-cyber-force","content_id":"4cf7deb2-1179-4211-aab8-0009176daa56","details":{"acronym":"NCF","brand":"ministry-of-justice","default_news_image":null,"logo":{"crest":"custom","formatted_title":"National <br/>Cyber Force","image":{"alt_text":"National Cyber Force","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61ba22cfd3bf7f055d72d837/NCF_2592_MASTER_STRAPLINE_AW__1__copy_cubic.png"}},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"National Cyber Force","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/national-cyber-force","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_contacts":[{"content_id":"3ec0445c-d554-401f-9873-ec4e758d22fb","details":{"contact_form_links":null,"description":null,"email_ad